# ===================================================================
# This repository contains ONLY the realtime inference add-on for
# LivePortrait.  Clone it alongside a full LivePortrait installation
# (which is the dependency) and these patterns will keep the upstream
# files from being accidentally committed.
# ===================================================================

# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
**/*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# Model weights
**/*.pth
**/*.onnx

pretrained_weights/

# Ipython notebook
*.ipynb

# Temporary files or benchmark resources
animations/*
tmp/*
.vscode/
**/*.DS_Store
gradio_temp/**

# Windows dependencies
ffmpeg/
LivePortrait_env/

# -------------------------------------------------------------------
# Upstream LivePortrait source (installed separately as a dependency)
# -------------------------------------------------------------------
src/
assets/
inference.py
inference_animals.py
app.py
app_animals.py
speed.py

# Upstream docs / meta (our README is README_REALTIME.md)
readme.md
readme_zh_cn.md
update.md
LICENSE

# Upstream requirements (ours is requirements_realtime.txt)
requirements.txt
requirements_base.txt
requirements_macOS.txt
